title: NDFD NOAA, Wave height forecast after Gustav landfall along Lousiana coast on Sept 02, 2008, USA, Aug 30, 2008
name: NDFD NOAA, Wave height forecast after Gustav landfall along Lousiana coast on Sept 02, 2008, USA, Aug 30, 2008
description:
The point shapefile shows the rise in sea-levels forecast as significant wave heights when Gustav makes landfall along Lousiana coast-line on 2nd Sept, 2008.
The shape file is generated from the NDFD (National Digital Forecast Database) 7 day-forecast as of 30th Aug, 2008.
